article.title: ZeroTemplate
article.text:
=ZeroNet Template=

Template for creating and developing ZeroNet sites.

It supports NPM dependencies and it uses Gulp and Browserify for bundling scripts. It also supports SASS and automatic deployments with Travis CI.

Project is available on [https://github.com/filips123/ GitHub] and [http://127.0.0.1:43110/1Aob9QXahTnn6iBriSSQ6qg8qXkHdkaX2x/ GitCenter]. It is licensed under MIT license.
